#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.phonebook.metainfo.xml:4
msgid "Phonebook"
msgstr "Agenda telefònica"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.phonebook.metainfo.xml:5
msgid "View and edit contacts"
msgstr "Visualitza i edita els contactes"

#. (itstool) path: component/developer_name
#: org.kde.phonebook.metainfo.xml:8
msgid "KDE Community"
msgstr "La comunitat KDE"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.phonebook.metainfo.xml:10
msgid ""
"Convergent contact management application for both desktop and mobile "
"devices."
msgstr ""
"Una aplicació convergent de gestió de contactes tant per a l'escriptori com "
"per a dispositius mòbils."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.phonebook.metainfo.xml:11
msgid ""
"It provides a central place for starting conversations. Depending on the "
"information available about a contact, respective actions are displayed."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona un punt central per a iniciar conversacions. En funció de la "
"informació disponible quant a un contacte, es mostren les accions "
"respectives."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
